  "description": "<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/09/26/14c548dfa38f8d6dc4c6235d2e244a18.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">本系列的第一部分的文章（&quot;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/search/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%A0%87%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E8%AF%B4/\" target=\"_blank\">英语音标这样说</a>&quot;），我们采用&ldquo;单兵作战&rdquo;的方式，详细介绍了元音的发音要领；第二部分（&quot;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/search/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%A0%87%E5%88%AB%E6%B7%B7%E6%B7%86/\" target=\"_blank\">英语音标别混淆</a>&quot;），我们用的是&ldquo;捉对厮杀&rdquo;的战术，通过元音之间一对一的比较，梳理元音的发音要领和区别。之前的几篇文章已经介绍了&ldquo;</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p797032/\" style=\"line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\">/iː/ vs. /ɪ/</a><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p803374/\" style=\"line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\">/ɪ/ vs.&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p803374/\" style=\"line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\">/e/</a><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p807075/\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/e/ vs. /</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p807075/\" target=\"_blank\">&aelig;/</a>&rdquo;、&ldquo;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p807137/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p807137/\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\"><font face=\"verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">&aelig;</span></font><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\">/ vs. /</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">ʌ</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p807137/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a>&rdquo;、</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p813688/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p813688/\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\"><font face=\"verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">&aelig;/ vs. /</span></font><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">ɑː</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p813688/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a>&rdquo;、</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p819286/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p819286/\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\"><font face=\"verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">&aelig;/ vs. /</span></font><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">ɒ</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p819286/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a>&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p819290/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/ɒ</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/ vs.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p819290/\" target=\"_blank\">ɔː/</a>&rdquo;和&ldquo;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831180/\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831180/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">ɒ</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">/ vs. /</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">ɔː</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">/</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">，本篇继续顺藤摸瓜，从</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.2px;\">ʊ</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">出发，找/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">uː</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">的发音要领！</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t【发音要领】</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/09/21/93953dd7e45e82c0792790f6f2b1b72e.jpg\" style=\"height: 373px; width: 500px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先看上面这张图的舌位变化。元音</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">/ʊ/和/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">uː</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">/都属于后元音，也就是说发音时都应该将舌头向喉咙的方向往后拉，最高点在舌头后部；而二者相比之下，</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">uː</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">/的舌后部抬得非常高，嘴唇的形状也收得更小</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">。实际上，/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">uː/这个音在英语里是舌头后部抬得最高的一个音。尝试感受舌头几乎完全挡住了咽喉，一用力甚至有想吐的感觉，那就对啦！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">比较一下两个音标的发音：</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">ʊ</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">/ vs. /</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">uː/</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><br />\n\t</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831191\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px;\">【单词辨音】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831191\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">look luke<br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">pull pool</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">full fool<br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">could cooed<br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">would&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/woo\" target=\"_blank\">woo</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">ed<br />\n\t<br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">【短句对比】<br />\n\t</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831191\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a><br />\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">Look, a new moon! /&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">Luke, a new moon!</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">The sign said 'pull'. /&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">The sign said 'pool'.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><br />\n\tThis isn't really full proof. /&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">This isn't really&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/foolproof\" target=\"_blank\">foolproof</a><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">The bird could. / The bird cooed.<br />\n\tHe would, Julie, at the full moon. /&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">He wooed Julie at the full moon.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831191/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p831191\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p829503/\">跟中国新歌声学英文：郑迦文Lost Stars</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"htt